"};\n"
"\n"
"Server::type_signal_something Server::signal_something()\n"
"{\n"
"  return m_signal_something;\n"
"}\n"

#: C/gtkmm-tutorial-in.xml:8289(para)
msgid ""
"You could just declare that signal as a public member variable, but some "
